{"tid":1098874,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"(勇於挑戰)C朗轉平價隊挑戰歐聯，美斯繼續溫室貴價隊","createTime":"2019-04-09T11:30:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-17T03:59:45.000Z","uid":173952,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"d411ac9cea394fff2cab39b78d416851c3afa3f2","tid":1098874,"uid":173952,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:30:43.000Z","msg":"歐聯8強明天就將開打，轉會市場統計了8支球隊的總身價，巴塞以11.8億歐排名第一，曼城則以4000萬歐之差屈居第二。<br />\n<br />\n巴塞和曼城也是僅有的兩支球隊身價超過10億歐的球隊，第三的利物浦總身價為9.505億歐。第四的熱刺為8.355億歐，曼聯7.96億歐排第五。前五的球隊，英超佔據了四席。儘管有了C.朗拿度的加入，但祖記7.825億歐的總身價只排在了第六。第七的是阿積士4.195億歐，第八的波圖全隊身價只有2.901億歐。<br />\n<br />\n歐聯8強球隊身價排行：（歐元）<br />\n<br />\n1。巴塞：11.8億<br />\n<br />\n2。曼城：11.4億<br />\n<br />\n3。利物浦：9.505億<br />\n<br />\n4。熱刺：8.355億<br />\n<br />\n5。曼聯：7.96億<br />\n<br />\n6。祖記：7.825億<br />\n<br />\n7。阿積士：4.195億<br />\n<br />\n8。波圖：2.901億"},{"pid":"ac3447dae8740160825a13ce31f4b5f033f283e0","tid":1098874,"uid":7027,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"熱刺仲高過曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed92a1048518a1ec178ae6ef1e9468ce3fa94efe","tid":1098874,"uid":213628,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:32:14.000Z","msg":"曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6fe73fef085848f96e19664be8068b056fee9bc5","tid":1098874,"uid":213628,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ac3447dae8740160825a13ce31f4b5f033f283e0","tid":1098874,"uid":7027,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:31:57.000Z","msg":"熱刺仲高過曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:33:07.000Z","msg":"其實正常<br />\n普巴同迪基亞值咁貴之外<br />\n其他後生都唔係好貴"},{"pid":"f6645b79299cb6f6624c72fdde1afd7cb9c59d35","tid":1098874,"uid":143940,"like":16,"dislike":3,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-09T11:34:00.000Z","msg":"垃圾蛆用哂啲錢過戶俾球證<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" cl